{"tid":1947393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［原告變被告］德國係俾支那人傳染武漢肺炎 但支那有傳病毒係來自德國","createTime":"2020-03-28T08:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T11:43:15.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1d5d47ae8a466ae6a751c20709d528d9341a0e","tid":1947393,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"俾支國員工傳入：<br />\n<br />\n據彭博社2月12日文章指，Webasto一位到德國總部參加會議的中國雇員，在1月20日到達德國後，有輕微感冒症狀，該雇員以為是飛行時差導致。可她在1月23日返回中國後又開始發燒，檢測後呈中共病毒陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n與這位中國員工同時參加會議的一位德國雇員，於1月27日出現感冒症狀，繼而被確認感染了中共病毒。接下來韋巴斯托在慕尼黑，和另外兩個德國城市分公司的多名員工，相繼出現病毒感染症狀，其中兩人把病毒傳給了他們的子女和妻子。<br />\n<br />\n截止2月11日，韋巴斯托公司雇員和家人感染中共病毒的人數達到16人，這是當時中共病毒在中國大陸以外最大的一個人傳人群組。<br />\n<br />\nWebasto公司所在的巴伐利亞州（Barvaria）是德國感染中共病毒和死亡人數第二多的州，截至3月23日，全州感染人數達到5,719，27人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n專家：中共病毒穿越國界傳到意大利<br />\n<br />\n儘管Webasto及時採取隔離員工，和關閉工作場所等措施，但這並不能阻止中共病毒在慕尼黑和整個巴伐利亞州的迅速傳播。<br />\n<br />\n從2月24日開始，中共病毒在巴伐利亞開始肆虐，至3月23日已造成該州的感染和死亡人數，分別佔全國相應比例的20%和30%，並成為德國疫情重災區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/3/24/n11970913.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F3%2F24%2Fn11970913.htm&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=33a0bde9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/3/24/n11970913.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n依家屈德國<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEBtsVN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEBtsVN.jpg&h=33818c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順手幫solomon簽聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-president-donald-trump-hold-chinas-government-accountable-coronavirus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-president-donald-trump-hold-chinas-government-accountable-coronavirus&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=e149493f\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-president-donald-trump-hold-chinas-government-accountable-coronavirus</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1243524708626075649?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1243524708626075649%3Fs%3D21&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=a94c8168\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1243524708626075649%3Fs%3D21&h=54b66420\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1243524708626075649?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"31d9440e4579ed7674e843b3bcd9d62419026e37","tid":1947393,"uid":53019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"持德國護照的大陸人 = 德國人"},{"pid":"cecdec3387dbf57d6fcafc5e82c67100f49d44db","tid":1947393,"uid":153689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T09:07:37.000Z","msg":"依篇文似假膠，不過應該有好多濕鳩真心膠會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1222b05c788c1692692b5966a9b53b89827fa1ca","tid":1947393,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ff9a5b1b156dfcf402790c485598fa4d311594","tid":1947393,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:43:15.000Z","msg":"push"}]}